Course is divided between meeting with individual film teams and independent film exercises. The course finishes with a screening of completed works.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to go through all the stages of making a short film together with a coordinator and to finish a short film or another film-based short form.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing the course, the student: -is acquainted with all the stages of making a short film - can run a small film team on its own, prepare the necessary materials for shoot - has a filmmaking experience and can analyze the completed short film from film-technical perspective.
